{"tid":1451711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚發夢由尖沙咀夢遊到葵芳嘅入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-11T20:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T16:51:19.000Z","uid":212884,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"02ec3d1c9f466446db29060f63e570e3c14d3a4b","tid":1451711,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:14:46.000Z","msg":"啱啱恰左一恰 發夢有人同我講<br />\n大約2100左右果陣 葵芳地鐵站第一次鎖站嘅時候<br />\n因為本身有乘客諗住用去荃灣方向最後一班經葵芳站嘅車 （當時未知果班係最後一班經葵芳站嘅車）比站入面嘅乘客搭車走<br />\n所以企喺車門中間爭取時間比街坊上車<br />\n咁呢班車嘅狗鐵車長為左成功開車離開車站<br />\n呃鳩乘客話暫時後面d車都會停葵芳站<br />\n所以企喺車門中間嘅乘客入番車廂<br />\n車長順利開到車 點知呢班車開左之後 後面d車飛站<br />\n搞到喺葵芳站嘅街坊冇路走 焗食有可能致命嘅tear gas<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈譴責狗鐵再一次危害市民安全！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8af4d69c4d10ec50092bcdbb68049451dfd9b55f","tid":1451711,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:12.000Z","msg":"自推到搵到呢班車嘅荃灣線車長出黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c643ffea269d2897adbd2c7e7b69300c1332e3","tid":1451711,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:22.000Z","msg":"自推到搵到呢班車嘅荃灣線車長出黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8422d8b5cf4ea13a522c6e18c7dfe6609c009a25","tid":1451711,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:32.000Z","msg":"自推到搵到呢班車嘅荃灣線車長出黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c934589783413564973e9c1f71045efb811d850","tid":1451711,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:21:21.000Z","msg":"休息得果幾個字 就比呢個夢搞到我瞓唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-larg